# ============================================================================
# BFSNet Docker Build Context Exclusions
# ============================================================================
# This file specifies which files and directories should be excluded from
# the Docker build context to speed up builds and reduce image size.
#
# Place this file in the docker/ directory and reference it with:
#   docker build -f docker/Dockerfile .
#
# Or copy to project root as .dockerignore for default behavior.
# ============================================================================

